room_title: Escape room "Game of Espionage" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Lansing
review: I’ve done The Ringmasters Den and Game of Espionage. They were both well set up. Just challenging enough. Can’t wait to go back and do the Zombie Roadhouse.

room_title: Escape room "Game of Espionage" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Lansing
review: The Game of Espionage was fantastic!! We had such a great time and the puzzles and challenges were so much fun. Highly recommended!
